    <item>
      <title>DEI 是什么？为什么它会受到攻击？</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/what-is-dei-kamala-harris-and-the-controversy-over-diversity-policies</link>
      <description><![CDATA[自从副总统卡马拉·哈里斯成为民主党新任美国总统候选人以来，共和党人就将她称为“多元化人才”，暗示她的晋升是因为她种族和性别，而不是她的智力或能力。支持共和党候选人、前总统唐纳德·特朗普的特斯拉公司首席执行官埃隆·马斯克甚至在他的社交网络 X 上分享了一则虚假广告，其中哈里斯的声音被篡改，称她是“多元化人才的终极代表”。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/what-is-dei-kamala-harris-and-the-controversy-over-diversity-policies</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 22:52:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>马杜罗指责委内瑞拉反对派策划武装袭击</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</link>
      <description><![CDATA[委内瑞拉政府指责反对派伪造选举记录，声称其候选人击败了总统尼古拉斯·马杜罗，并警告称，据称周六将在被禁领导人玛丽亚·科里娜·马查多呼吁和平示威的地方附近发生武装袭击。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/maduro-gets-electoral-council-nod-in-bid-to-legitimize-victory</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 19:08:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国司法部加大力度避免选举混乱</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国司法部正在为 11 月的总统大选做准备，该部正在关注投票权斗争、调查威胁，并准备恢复与社交媒体公司的简报，以遏制错误信息的传播。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/us-justice-department-steps-up-efforts-to-avoid-election-mayhem</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 17:03:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>菲律宾加强南海前哨十年防御</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/philippines-fortifies-south-china-sea-outpost-to-last-a-decade</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据四位知情人士透露，菲律宾已对在有争议的南海搁浅的一艘二战时期的舰船进行了大规模增援，增援程度足以使这艘与北京关系紧张的前哨基地至少再维持十年。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-08-02/philippines-fortifies-south-china-sea-outpost-to-last-a-decade</guid>
      <pubDate>Fri, 02 Aug 2024 06:20:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
